    "Due to the need for a large pool of participants in the evaluation, we only select the top 5 T2V methods for voting.",
    "We finally collected 185 valid questionnaires.",
    "The results in Fig. 6a demonstrate that our method significantly outperforms other leading T2V methods.",
    "Furthermore, MagicTime significantly enhances the quality of metamorphic videos, confirming the effectiveness of encoding physical knowledge through training with metamorphic videos.",
